OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAnother generally fair days
OL,6,Fweather in prospect. Mostly dry with
OL,7,Fperiods of sunshine through the
OL,8,Fmorning, before turning hazy from the
OL,9,Fwest during the afternoon. Winds light.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry with some late brightness
OL,12,Faround the Moray Firth this evening.
OL,13,FMeanwhile light and patchy rain moves
OL,14,Finto the west, before spreading
OL,15,Fnortheast through the rest of the
OL,16,Fnight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
