OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FRather cloudy with a few
OL,6,Fspots of light rain, but mainly dry
OL,7,Fwith some bright spells around the
OL,8,FMoray Firth. Showery outbreaks of rain
OL,9,Fwill then develop into the evening.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,12,Ffairly unsettled and changeable few
OL,13,Fdays with a series of showery or
OL,14,Foccasionally more persistent bands of
OL,15,Frain spreading up from the southwest
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
